FY_BingDog


This is a map I made a long ago. It was there, finished but in the folder with all my projects it was like a needle in a haystack. I recalled that it and searched for the map. Now I gave it a name and decided to upload it.

It's not looking very good but it's really fun map I've played with friends and the gameplay isn't as bad as I expected. It will suit very good in all types of servers (deathmatch, classic etc)
